\[ \begin{align*} \text{Odds ratio} = \frac{\left( \frac{n+1}{\text{total}+1} \right)_{\text{Text A}} }{ \left( \frac{n+1}{\text{total}+1} \right)_{\text{Text B}} } \end{align*} \]
